Author: KsaAZaks
Title: [ANN][ICO] ðŸ’£ OctoBit.IO - Online Wallet & Advertising Network ready to go ðŸ’£
Body: Today, on June 23, 2018, the pre-ICO of OctoBit.IO project has ended.  Unfortunately, we managed to collect only 10% of the planned amount, but nevertheless during the last month our wallet was field-tested. More than 5000 users joined us. All found bugs were fixed and many new features were added. Nevertheless, crowfunding has failed and now we have to change our plans:  And here's what we'll do next:  1. First of all, our coin "OctoBit Coin" (OCTO) will be released and will be used in our products. 2. In order not to waste time, new ICO won't be conducted! 3. We will conduct a large-scale AIRDROP on all coins that have not been sold. 4. All participants in the bounty campaign will receive coins as planned. 5. To compensate the free distribution of coins, all our investors will receive X10 coins from the amount that they initially bought. 6. We will continue the development of our products.   A total of 100 million coins will be issued, they will be distributed as follows:  22% Sold coins to investors 5% Project team 6% Bounty 5% Advisers 62% AIRDROP   We are inviting everyone to participate in one of the largest AIRDROPs in 2018 with a pool of $750,000.  https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4183451

Author: KsaAZaks
Title: [ANN][ICO] ðŸ’£ OctoBit.IO - Online Wallet & Advertising Network ready to go ðŸ’£
Body: Today, on June 23, 2018, the pre-ICO of OctoBit.IO project has ended.  Unfortunately, we managed to collect only 10% of the planned amount, but nevertheless during the last month our wallet was field-tested. More than 5000 users joined us. All found bugs were fixed and many new features were added. Nevertheless, crowfunding has failed and now we have to change our plans:  And here's what we'll do next:  1. First of all, our coin "OctoBit Coin" (OCTO) will be released and will be used in our products. 2. In order not to waste time, new ICO won't be conducted! 3. We will conduct a large-scale AIRDROP on all coins that have not been sold. 4. All participants in the bounty campaign will receive coins as planned. 5. To compensate the free distribution of coins, all our investors will receive X10 coins from the amount that they initially bought. 6. We will continue the development of our products.   A total of 100 million coins will be issued, they will be distributed as follows:  22% Sold coins to investors 5% Project team 6% Bounty 5% Advisers 62% AIRDROP   We are inviting everyone to participate in one of the largest AIRDROPs in 2018 with a pool of $750,000.  https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=4183451  OctoBit Coin site & wallets: https://coin.octobit.io  OctoBit Coin explorer: http://explorer.octobit.io:8080
